; ShrinkConditions: have_ping is set unconditionally from the ping receive,
; so DropSetConditions should fire and the test on out's clause should die.
; Minimal shape: a zero-arity condition tested in a clause that also
; positively receives a view.

#message ping(i32 X).
#query out(free i32 X).

have_ping : ping(_).
out(X) : have_ping, ping(X).
